column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/43560abbfe38d563bb4433269362179496df3790 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
Please make transaction changes on transifex (https://www.transifex.com/projects/p/bitcoin/). We regularly pull translation changes from there before releases.\n
